@startuml API Logs Plugin Workflow

!theme crt-amber
left to right direction

title Fluxion Logs Plugin - Code Flow and Actions

participant "Application" as app
participant "IFluxionLogsPlugin" as plugin
participant "LogStorage" as storage

== Plugin Initialization ==
app -> plugin: OnEnable(OnEnableData)
plugin -> storage: Initialize log storage
storage --> plugin: Ready

== Log Import ==
app -> plugin: ImportLogs(filesystem::path)
plugin -> storage: Parse and store logs
storage --> plugin: Import complete

== Filter Application ==
app -> plugin: ApplyFilters(filters, highlight_only)
plugin -> storage: Apply filter conditions
storage --> plugin: Filtering complete

== Navigation ==
app -> plugin: GetNextLog(filter_id)
plugin -> storage: Find next matching log
storage --> plugin: Return log index

== Rendering ==
app -> plugin: GetTableHeader()
plugin --> app: Return column structure

app -> plugin: GetLogs(ranges, out_logs_map)
plugin -> storage: Fetch log rows for ranges
storage --> plugin: Return log data
plugin --> app: Update out_logs_map

== Cleanup ==
app -> plugin: DisableFilters()
plugin -> storage: Clear filter state
storage --> plugin: Done

app -> plugin: OnDisable(OnDisableData)
plugin --> app: Cleanup complete

@enduml
